### ======================================================
### LINE Webhook & Health 手動測試檔案
### 使用方式：安裝 VS Code REST Client 擴充後，點擊 Send Request
###
### 簽章產生方式（X-Line-Signature）：
###   python3 -c "
###   import hmac, hashlib, base64
###   body = '<json body 原始字串>'
###   secret = '<LINE Channel Secret>'
###   sig = base64.b64encode(hmac.new(secret.encode(), body.encode(), hashlib.sha256).digest()).decode()
###   print(sig)
###   "
### ======================================================

### 共用變數（切換環境只需改 baseUrl）
@baseUrlProd    = https://mrvshop-func.azurewebsites.net/api
@baseUrlStaging = https://mrvshop-func-staging.azurewebsites.net/api
@baseUrl        = {{baseUrlProd}}

# 填入 LINE Channel Secret（僅本機測試用，勿 commit）
@lineChannelSecret = YOUR_LINE_CHANNEL_SECRET

# 測試用 LINE User ID（可填自己的 LINE UID）
@testUserId = Uxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Health Check（無需簽章，確認服務是否正常）
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Health Check - Staging
GET {{baseUrlStaging}}/health

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 2. Webhook 連通測試（空事件陣列）
#    LINE Developer Console 按下 Verify 時發送的格式
#    ⚠️  需要填入正確的 X-Line-Signature，否則回傳 401
#    快速產生：
#      BODY='{"destination":"Utest","events":[]}'
#      python3 -c "import hmac,hashlib,base64; print(base64.b64encode(hmac.new('YOUR_SECRET'.encode(), '$BODY'.encode(), hashlib.sha256).digest()).decode())"
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Webhook Verify（空事件 - 模擬 LINE Verify 按鈕）
# 填入正確 signature 後送出，應回傳 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/LineWebhook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Line-Signature: REPLACE_WITH_VALID_SIGNATURE

{
  "destination": "Utest123",
  "events": []
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 3. 模擬真實 LINE 訊息事件
#    ⚠️  需要有效 X-Line-Signature
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### 模擬用戶傳送文字訊息（需有效 signature）
POST {{baseUrl}}/LineWebhook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Line-Signature: REPLACE_WITH_VALID_SIGNATURE

{
  "destination": "Utest123",
  "events": [
    {
      "type": "message",
      "message": {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "999999999",
        "text": "你好，請問幾天到貨？"
      },
      "webhookEventId": "test-event-001",
      "deliveryContext": { "isRedelivery": false },
      "timestamp": 1708502400000,
      "source": {
        "type": "user",
        "userId": "{{testUserId}}"
      },
      "replyToken": "EXPIRED_REPLY_TOKEN_WILL_FALLBACK_TO_PUSH",
      "mode": "active"
    }
  ]
}

### 模擬查詢訂單物流
POST {{baseUrl}}/LineWebhook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Line-Signature: REPLACE_WITH_VALID_SIGNATURE

{
  "destination": "Utest123",
  "events": [
    {
      "type": "message",
      "message": {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "999999998",
        "text": "我的貨到哪裡了？2月15號下單的"
      },
      "webhookEventId": "test-event-002",
      "deliveryContext": { "isRedelivery": false },
      "timestamp": 1708502400000,
      "source": {
        "type": "user",
        "userId": "{{testUserId}}"
      },
      "replyToken": "EXPIRED_REPLY_TOKEN_WILL_FALLBACK_TO_PUSH",
      "mode": "active"
    }
  ]
}

### 模擬要求退款（測試婉拒流程）
POST {{baseUrl}}/LineWebhook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Line-Signature: REPLACE_WITH_VALID_SIGNATURE

{
  "destination": "Utest123",
  "events": [
    {
      "type": "message",
      "message": {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "999999997",
        "text": "斷貨了，我要退款"
      },
      "webhookEventId": "test-event-003",
      "deliveryContext": { "isRedelivery": false },
      "timestamp": 1708502400000,
      "source": {
        "type": "user",
        "userId": "{{testUserId}}"
      },
      "replyToken": "EXPIRED_REPLY_TOKEN_WILL_FALLBACK_TO_PUSH",
      "mode": "active"
    }
  ]
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
